pull.title: Optimize secp256k1_fe_normalize_weak calls.
pull.body: Move secp256k1_fe_normalize_weak calls out of ECMULT_TABLE_GET_GE and ECMULT_TABLE_GET_GE_STORAGE and into secp256k1_ge_globalz_set_table_gej instead.

repo.name: secp256k1
repo.description: Optimized C library for EC operations on curve secp256k1

repo.name: secp256k1

events.message:
Optimize secp256k1_fe_normalize_weak calls.
Move secp256k1_fe_normalize_weak calls out of ECMULT_TABLE_GET_GE and ECMULT_TABLE_GET_GE_STORAGE and into secp256k1_ge_globalz_set_table_gej instead.
